name: New Balance Men's Impact Run Jacket
description: Stay prepared on your run with our Impact Run Jacket. The nylon woven shell features wind and water resistance for protection in unpredictable weather, plus this men's running jacket can be packed up into a waist-pack when conditions heat up. It's finished with reflective branding and piping and a graphic print for added style.

Featuring a breathable and lightweight fabric, the top also implements a higher neck design to help protect against the wind. Additionally, the front zip allows the runner to unzip the front and experience better ventilation. Supporting a more sustainable design approach, this 1/2 zip top is also constructed with recycled materials.
